snippet.title: Blossom Tales (Switch) Debut Trailer
snippet.description: Blossom Tales is coming This Winter as a console exclusive to the Nintendo Switch. Enjoy an awesome 10+ hours retro inspired Action RPG starring Lily, Knight of the Rose on her quest to save the king!
